title: Watch as Average Americans Are Convinced That Rob Kardashian Is the Supreme Court Nominee
text:
Talk show host Jimmy Kimmel took to the streets to see how many people would believe that Rob Kardashian was Trump's Supreme Court nominee. Of course, Rob is not the pick; Trump's SCOTUS nominee is Neil Gorsuch , who is honestly an even more frightening choice than Rob if you care about women's rights.
 But anyway! Please enjoy how politically savvy these American citizens are and weep for the constitution!
